Dinesh Patel has just been granted R10,000 bail. (eNCA) JOHANNESBURG - Dinesh Patel has been granted R10,000 bail. He is the brother-in-law of Gupta ally, Iqbal Sharma. READ: PP finds Magashule's conduct in Vrede project amounts to maladministration And is the latest suspect to be charged in connection with the notorious Vrede Dairy Project in the Free State. While Sharma remains behind bars, Patel won his freedom a little earlier. He has been charged with fraud and money laundering, too.